title: Cherry Li
text: Hello! My name is Cherry Li, and I am a second-year Statistics and Data Science student at UCLA. I am looking to pursue a career in the actuarial industry and hoping to make meaningful contributions there using what data science has to offer. You can learn more about me from my resume.
